Larry, if I can hear it, its too loud.

7
00:01:21,495 --> 00:01:24,555
Too loud. Too loud.

8
00:01:24,664 --> 00:01:27,633
This music is Beethoven to me, ma!

9
00:03:18,411 --> 00:03:22,507
Sataka, it's time to call the White.

10
00:03:25,986 --> 00:03:27,453
Ow!

11
00:03:41,334 --> 00:03:42,995
WOO!

12
00:03:52,178 --> 00:03:54,271
Chainsaws? A ringing sound?

13
00:03:54,381 --> 00:03:55,871
Its more like a whine.

14
00:03:55,982 --> 00:03:56,971
That frying?

15
00:03:57,083 --> 00:03:59,813
Frying and then a chopping sound,
like an axe on a tree.

16
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,512
Chk! Chk!

