23
00:04:23,076 --> 00:04:26,341
Leprosy is entirely curable.

24
00:04:27,247 --> 00:04:28,646
Don't worry about the ear.

25
00:04:28,748 --> 00:04:30,079
Nothing for it anyway.

26
00:04:30,183 --> 00:04:32,208
It's my instrument.

27
00:04:32,319 --> 00:04:34,651
They use to call me Big Ear in Africa.

28
00:04:34,754 --> 00:04:36,312
They won't be calling you
anything anymore,

29
