Mergh.

33
00:04:50,170 --> 00:04:51,899
Mergh.

34
00:04:53,373 --> 00:04:55,341
What if I stayed in America?

35
00:04:55,442 --> 00:04:57,603
I'll never complete my catalog.

36
00:04:58,044 --> 00:05:00,945
Only one instrument left to get.

37
00:05:01,348 --> 00:05:02,906
Molimo.

38
00:05:03,016 --> 00:05:05,951
Holy Grail of Pygmy music.

39
00:05:15,729 --> 00:05:17,390
I gotta see Lydia.

40
