So interesting.

43
00:05:37,217 --> 00:05:40,846
Lydia, my liver is shot.

44
00:05:40,954 --> 00:05:43,149
I've got one more trip left in me,

45
00:05:43,256 --> 00:05:45,281
I need the Malimo.

46
00:05:45,692 --> 00:05:47,023
And it's not expensive.

47
00:05:47,761 --> 00:05:50,195
Africa, Africa.

48
00:05:52,098 --> 00:05:53,895
You don't have cash?

49
00:05:56,503 --> 00:05:57,561
Ow.

50
00:05:58,338 --> 00:05:59,464
Thank you.

51
00:06:04,210 --> 00:06:05,142
Sataka.

52
00:06:59,265 --> 00:07:00,823
Well you have to include the Dogon,

53
00:07:00,934 --> 00:07:02,561
The Dogon? -Yes.

54
00:07:02,669 --> 00:07:05,035
You, you really want to include them?

55
00:07:05,338 --> 00:07:07,067
They're not endangered peoples.

56
00:07:07,173 --> 00:07:09,835
The Dogon are not endangered?

57
00:07:09,943 --> 00:07:12,571
How many of them can there possibly be?

58
